The course aims at developing written and oral Estonian at level C1.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The course aims at developing written and oral Estonian at level C1.  Estonian reading comprehension and summarizing skills are developed. An overview on the structure of the Estonian language will be provided in the context of language learning.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Student who has completed the course *	knows the difference between standard language and language for special purposes; *	is able to quickly grasp the content and relevance of a wide range of news, articles, and overviews on specialized topics; *	is able to give a review of complex texts; is able to summarize and comment on these texts; *	is able to express him/herself clearly and concisely in written communication;  *	is able to describe, discuss, give an opinion, and comment within the themes to be learned, while using linguistic knowledge for the purposes intended.
